videos.description: K.yle Benton slams it home off the feed from Del'Vin Dickerson.
videos.headline: Great ball movement from NC Central as Dickerson hits Benton for dunk

videos.description: Great ball movement from the Spartans finds the driving Kevin Okaro who draws the contact and converts the basket.
videos.headline: Norfolk State beats the trap as Okaro coverts the and-one

videos.description: Patrick Cole somehow scores over multiple defenders to even the score.
videos.headline: NC Centrals' Patrick Cole hits the off-balance circus shot

videos.description: Eagle's Rashun Madison somehow ties up the charging Spartan's Zanyah Robinson
videos.headline: NC Centrals' Madison ties up Robinson to stop the Norfolk State break.

videos.description: North Carolina Central Eagles celebrate their 67-59 victory over Norfolk State.
videos.headline: North Carolina Central goes dancing for the second time in school history.

videos.description: North Carolina Central punches its ticket to the NCAA tournament by defeating Norfolk State 67-59.
videos.headline: NC Central captures MEAC title

videos.description: NCCU's Coach Moton describes his team's tremendous defensive effort in their win over Norfolk State.
videos.headline: NC Central's head coach Le'velle Moton discusses his Eagles going dancing
